Source: crudeoidc
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Univention GmbH <packages@univention.de>
Build-Depends:
 debhelper,
 dh-autoreconf,
 libglib2.0-0,
 libpam0g-dev,
 libsasl2-dev,
 librhonabwy-dev (>= 1.1.2),
 quilt,
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: cy2-oidc
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: SASL plugin for OIDC authentication
 This package contains a SASL plugin that performs a crude
 check on a OIDC ID-Token. The JWT signature and date
 are verified, and access is granted on behalf to the user taken for a
 configurable attribute.

Package: pam-oidc
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: PAM module for OIDC authentication
 This package contains a PAM module that performs a crude
 check on a OIDC ID-Token. The JWT signature and date
 are verified, and access is granted on behalf to the user taken for a
 configurable attribute.
